Package com.pandora.controllers.responsebodies.services

Interface SpeciesResponseService

All Known Implementing Classes:
SpeciesResponseServiceImpl
public interface SpeciesResponseService
The SpeciesResponseService interface defines the contract for services responsible for post-processing species-related responses and converting them into the appropriate format represented by SpeciesResponse. Implementing classes are expected to provide the logic for post-processing specie information.
Version:
0.0.1
Author:
Wim Joost van Hoek
